<mxCell id="pol" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color='#FFCD5A'&gt;Policy · GET /v0.1/servers&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color='#82C8FF'&gt;INBOUND&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;• cors  origin:* · GET, OPTIONS · headers: Authorization, Content-Type&lt;br&gt;• cache-lookup  (TTL 60–300 s)&lt;br&gt;• authentication-managed-identity&lt;br&gt;    resource = https://azure-apicenter.net&lt;br&gt;• set-backend-service → API Center data plane&lt;br&gt;• rewrite-uri /workspaces/default/...&lt;br&gt;• set-header Authorization: Bearer @(token)&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color='#82C8FF'&gt;OUTBOUND&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;• set-body → MCP v0.1 projection { servers[] }&lt;br&gt;• cache-store  duration = 120 s&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color='#98A0AC'&gt;Retired vs POC: ARM call (control plane)&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#26282E;strokeColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=10;fontSize=10;fontColor=#E2E6EC;fontFamily=Courier New;arcSize=6;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="102.2" y="563.8" width="1009.8" height="202.0" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
